title: SummerHouse: Luke, I Am Your Fourth Wall
description:
The triumphant and messy second installment of the Summer House reunion is fantastic, if lacking some important questions and topics. So sad to see this epic season end.Be sure to check this episode out with Crappens on Demand. This was you can watch us podcast, not just listen: https://www.patreon.com/posts/50984236

Our Patreon Extras: https://patreon.com/watchwhatcrappens
